Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:02.43,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:04.01,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,菲魯特 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.88,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 你搆得到掉在這裡面的百圓硬幣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,既視感？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:11.86,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}劇場 {\1c&H000000&}其六
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:16.87,SignC,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}劇場{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}❻不是{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}豬的{\1c&HC2BA20&\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}願{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:15.76,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間做這種事了 和萊茵哈魯特那傢伙的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:16.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,又來？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:19.75,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,我在和他比誰能先夾到大人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,果真是和和睦睦相親相愛的劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.16,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,然後萊茵哈魯特不停夾到大人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲魯特卻一個都夾不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:30.38,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,只能拿到這百圓硬幣扭轉局勢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:33.64,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,我聽見了哪家喪家犬的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:35.87,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,我現在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.33,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,沒空理你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:38.53,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,即便看到這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:39.47,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,那個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:43.56,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,交給妾身的話此等玩樂宛若兒戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:45.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都能做到的人真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:50.99,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,雖然耳朵裡面吹進了你們吵鬧的廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:53.97,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的凡人 你就如此拘泥於勝負嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.20,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是無論如何都想贏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.66,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:02.32,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,對 無論如何都想得到這個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:05.20,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就把這個給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:09.36,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,你想要這個 而這個又在妾身手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.19,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你需要做的事情便只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.25,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,謝了啊普莉希拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 菲魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來說不定就能贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.24,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 你別低頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:24.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是低個頭就能解決的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:25.37,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妾身都還沒說到舔腳的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:31.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,你居然想說舔腳啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:32.71,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,所以 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.03,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,我不會低頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,菲魯特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:37.98,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,或許低頭了就能拿到人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:42.09,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,但這場比試說到底是我和萊茵哈魯特的比試
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:45.07,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,透過別人把東西讓給我來獲勝這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:48.25,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒辦法很好地表達 我總覺得這是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.02,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你那渺小的矜持占了上風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.35,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這就是我渺小的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:58.37,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果丟棄了它 感覺我就不再是我自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:01.49,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這也是一種活法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:05.30,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓妾身見識見識你掙扎的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.03,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,看到了掙扎的我你可別被嚇到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.87,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,那就盡情讓妾身驚詫來取悅妾身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.65,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,也謝謝小哥你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.50,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,我會用這枚硬幣一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.48,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,哦 一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,普莉希拉 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:23.66,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我能做到的 我要夾到一個人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:23.66,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes, I got one! I got a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.82,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,妾身並沒有做什麼值得被感謝的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:24.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.62,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}來吧人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come on! Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.97,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,人偶堵住了出不來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:30.42,Default,Priscilla,0000,0000,0000,,盡情掙扎吧 盡情掙扎吧
